    <briefdescription>
<para>Shared context passed to all GUI programs. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Contains all data needed for rendering GUI programs. This structure acts as a dependency injection container, providing programs with access to world state, physics settings, inventory data, and entity interfaces without tight coupling. </para>
